                        <div class="q-main-content"><div class="q-text-inline"><span class="q-num">37</span><div><span>Cognitive training games can successfully double the actual structural volume of working memory.</span><br><select id="q37" class="user-ans"><option value="">---</option><option value="YES">YES</option><option value="NO">NO</option><option value="NOT GIVEN">NOT GIVEN</option></select></div></div></div>
                        <div class="explanation-box"><strong>Explanation:</strong> Đoạn G khẳng định việc kiểm toán cấu trúc não bộ cho thấy dung tích cấu trúc của bộ nhớ làm việc không thay đổi khi chơi game phần mềm luyện não: <i>"...the structural volume of the memory engine itself remains unchanged..."</i> Do đó chọn NO.</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="q-row" id="block-q38">
                        <div class="q-main-content"><div class="q-text-inline"><span class="q-num">38</span><div><span>Working memory capacity values vary significantly between specific geographical populations.</span><br><select id="q38" class="user-ans"><option value="">---</option><option value="YES">YES</option><option value="NO">NO</option><option value="NOT GIVEN">NOT GIVEN</option></select></div></div></div>
                        <div class="explanation-box"><strong>Explanation:</strong> Trong bài viết không có bất kỳ thông tin nào so sánh dung lượng bộ nhớ giữa các quần thể địa lý khác nhau. Do đó chọn NOT GIVEN.</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="q-row" id="block-q39">
                        <div class="q-main-content"><div class="q-text-inline"><span class="q-num">39</span><div><span>Auditory signal items inside the phonological loop last indefinitely without any internal rehearsal.</span><br><select id="q39" class="user-ans"><option value="">---</option><option value="YES">YES</option><option value="NO">NO</option><option value="NOT GIVEN">NOT GIVEN</option></select></div></div></div>
                        <div class="explanation-box"><strong>Explanation:</strong> Đoạn C nêu rõ nếu thiếu việc lặp lại thầm lặng (silent rehearsal), thông tin sẽ biến mất trong vòng vài giây: <i>"refreshing them continuously via silent vocal rehearsal... If this internal echo is disrupted... items deteriorate within seconds..."</i> Do đó chọn NO.</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="q-row" id="block-q40">
                        <div class="q-main-content"><div class="q-text-inline"><span class="q-num">40</span><div><span>Neurologists and software creators have now reached a absolute agreement regarding memory transfer benefits.</span><br><select id="q40" class="user-ans"><option value="">---</option><option value="YES">YES</option><option value="NO">NO</option><option value="NOT GIVEN">NOT GIVEN</option></select></div></div></div>
                        <div class="explanation-box"><strong>Explanation:</strong> Đoạn G khẳng định vấn đề này vẫn đang bị tranh luận dữ dội chứ chưa có sự đồng thuận tuyệt đối: <i>"Despite these insights, the exact boundaries of working memory training remain heavily contested."</i> Do đó chọn NO.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <footer>
        <div id="timer">60:00</div>
        <div class="nav-buttons">
            <button id="btn-prev" class="btn-nav" onclick="changePart(-1)" disabled>Previous Part</button>
            <button id="btn-next" class="btn-nav" onclick="changePart(1)">Next Part</button>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        let currentPart = 1;
        let totalTime = 60 * 60; 
        let timerInterval;
        
        const answerKey = {
            q1: "FALSE", q2: "TRUE", q3: "FALSE", q4: "FALSE", q5: "TRUE", q6: "FALSE", q7: "NOT GIVEN",
            q8: "sub-polar", q9: "deep", q10: "upwelling", q11: "benthic", q12: "gulf", q13: "thermohaline",
            q14: "ii", q15: "vi", q16: "vii", q17: "v", q18: "i", q19: "iv", q20: "iii",
            q21: "B", q22: "A", q23: "B", q24: "A", q25: "B", q26: "B",
            q27: "B", q28: "A", q29: "B", q30: "B", q31: "A", q32: "B",
            q33: "YES", q34: "NO", q35: "YES", q36: "NO", q37: "NO", q38: "NOT GIVEN", q39: "NO", q40: "NO"
        };

        function startTest() {
            const nameInput = document.getElementById('candidate-name').value.trim();
            if(!nameInput) {
                alert("Please enter your name to start the examination.");
                return;
            }
            document.getElementById('display-name').innerText = nameInput;
            document.getElementById('start-screen').style.display = 'none';
            startTimer();
            initHighlighter();
        }

        function startTimer() {
            timerInterval = setInterval(() => {
                totalTime--;
                let mins = Math.floor(totalTime / 60);
                let secs = totalTime % 60;
                
                document.getElementById('timer').innerText = 
                    `${mins.toString().padStart(2, '0')}:${secs.toString().padStart(2, '0')}`;
                
                if(totalTime <= 300) { 
                    document.getElementById('timer').style.color = '#fff';
                    document.getElementById('timer').style.backgroundColor = '#dc2626';
                }

                if (totalTime <= 0) {
                    clearInterval(timerInterval);
                    alert("Time is up! Your answers will be submitted automatically.");
                    submitTest(true);
                }
            }, 1000);
        }

        /* ================================================================
           ADVANCED HIGH LIGHTER CORE REWRITTEN SYSTEM (OPTIMIZED)
           ================================================================
        */
        let currentSavedRange = null;

        function initHighlighter() {
            const highlightMenu = document.getElementById('highlight-menu');

            // Lắng nghe sự kiện bôi đen chuột trong toàn hệ thống
            document.addEventListener('mouseup', (e) => {
                const selection = window.getSelection();
                const selectedText = selection.toString().trim();

                // Nếu click vào vùng đã bôi vàng -> Hiện menu xóa bôi
                if (e.target.classList.contains('ielts-highlight')) {
                    currentSavedRange = e.target;
                    highlightMenu.innerText = "Clear Highlight";
                    highlightMenu.style.left = `${e.clientX}px`;
                    highlightMenu.style.top = `${e.clientY - 35}px`;
                    highlightMenu.style.display = 'block';
                    return;
                }

                // Nếu chọn đoạn text mới hợp lệ bên vùng đọc bài (passage-side)
                if (selectedText !== '' && isInsidePassage(selection.anchorNode)) {
                    currentSavedRange = selection.getRangeAt(0).cloneRange();
                    highlightMenu.innerText = "Highlight";
                    highlightMenu.style.left = `${e.clientX}px`;
                    highlightMenu.style.top = `${e.clientY - 35}px`;
                    highlightMenu.style.display = 'block';
                } else {
                    highlightMenu.style.display = 'none';
                }
            });

            // Khi click chuột xuống ở bất kì đâu, ẩn menu bôi nếu không click trúng nút menu
            document.addEventListener('mousedown', (e) => {
                if (e.target !== highlightMenu) {
                    setTimeout(() => highlightMenu.style.display = 'none', 150);
                }
            });

            // Xử lý sự kiện click nút bôi vàng / xóa bôi vàng
            highlightMenu.addEventListener('click', () => {
                if (highlightMenu.innerText === "Highlight" && currentSavedRange) {
                    const span = document.createElement('span');
                    span.className = 'ielts-highlight';
                    try {
                        currentSavedRange.surroundContents(span);
                    } catch (err) {
                        // Fix lỗi nếu bôi lan sang các thẻ HTML lân cận
                        alert("Please select text strictly within a single paragraph element.");
                    }
                    window.getSelection().removeAllRanges();
                } 
                else if (highlightMenu.innerText === "Clear Highlight" && currentSavedRange) {
                    const parent = currentSavedRange.parentNode;
                    while (currentSavedRange.firstChild) {
                        parent.insertBefore(currentSavedRange.firstChild, currentSavedRange);
                    }
                    parent.removeChild(currentSavedRange);
                }
                highlightMenu.style.display = 'none';
            });
        }

        function isInsidePassage(node) {
            while (node) {
                if (node.classList && node.classList.contains('passage-side')) return true;
                node = node.parentNode;
            }
            return false;
        }

        /* End of Highlighter Engine Component Logic */

        function changePart(direction) {
            document.getElementById(`part${currentPart}`).classList.remove('active');
            currentPart += direction;
            document.getElementById(`part${currentPart}`).classList.add('active');

            document.getElementById('btn-prev').disabled = (currentPart === 1);
            document.getElementById('btn-next').disabled = (currentPart === 3);
            if(currentPart === 3) {
                document.getElementById('btn-next').innerText = "Finish";
                document.getElementById('btn-next').onclick = () => submitTest(false);
            } else {
                document.getElementById('btn-next').innerText = "Next Part";
                document.getElementById('btn-next').onclick = () => changePart(1);
            }
        }

        function submitTest(isAuto = false) {
            if(!isAuto) {
                let confirmSubmit = confirm("Are you sure you want to finish and submit your exam results?");
                if(!confirmSubmit) return;
            }
            
            clearInterval(timerInterval);
            document.body.classList.add('review-mode');
            let score = 0;

            for (let i = 1; i <= 40; i++) {
                let inputElement = document.getElementById(`q${i}`);
                if (inputElement) {
                    if (inputElement.tagName === "INPUT") {
                        inputElement.setAttribute('value', inputElement.value);
                    } else if (inputElement.tagName === "SELECT") {
                        for (let opt of inputElement.options) {
                            if (opt.value === inputElement.value) opt.setAttribute('selected', 'selected');
                            else opt.removeAttribute('selected');
                        }
                    }
                } else {
                    let radios = document.getElementsByName(`q${i}`);
                    for (let r of radios) {
                        if (r.checked) r.setAttribute('checked', 'checked');
                        else r.removeAttribute('checked');
                    }
                }
            }

            for (let i = 1; i <= 40; i++) {
                let userAns = "";
                let inputElement = document.getElementById(`q${i}`);
                
                if(inputElement) {
                    userAns = inputElement.value.trim().toLowerCase();
                } else {
                    let radios = document.getElementsByName(`q${i}`);
                    for(let r of radios) {
                        if(r.checked) userAns = r.value.toLowerCase();
                        r.disabled = true;
                    }
                }

                let targetKey = (answerKey[`q${i}`] || "").toLowerCase();
                let targetRow = document.getElementById(`block-q${i}`) || document.getElementById(`q${i}`)?.parentElement || document.getElementsByName(`q${i}`)[0]?.parentElement?.parentElement;
                
                if (userAns === targetKey) {
                    score++;
                    if(targetRow) {
                        let span = document.createElement('span');
                        span.className = "correct-ans";
                        span.innerText = ` ✓ Correct (${answerKey['q'+i]})`;
                        targetRow.querySelector('.q-main-content')?.appendChild(span) || targetRow.appendChild(span);
                    }
                } else {
                    if(targetRow) {
                        let span = document.createElement('span');
                        span.className = "correct-ans";
                        span.style.color = "red";
                        span.innerText = ` ✗ Incorrect (Correct: ${answerKey['q'+i]})`;
                        targetRow.querySelector('.q-main-content')?.appendChild(span) || targetRow.appendChild(span);
                    }
                }
            }

            document.getElementById('score-candidate-name').innerText = document.getElementById('display-name').innerText;
            document.getElementById('score-raw-out').innerText = `Result: ${score} / 40 Questions`;
            document.getElementById('score-band-out').innerText = calculateIELTSBand(score);
            
            document.getElementById('score-screen').style.display = 'flex';
            document.getElementById('btn-submit').style.display = 'none';
            document.getElementById('btn-download').style.display = 'block';
        }

        function closeScoreScreen() {
            document.getElementById('score-screen').style.display = 'none';
            currentPart = 1;
            changePart(0);
            document.getElementById('btn-prev').disabled = false;
            document.getElementById('btn-next').disabled = false;
            document.getElementById('btn-next').innerText = "Next Part";
            document.getElementById('btn-next').onclick = () => changePart(1);
        }

        function calculateIELTSBand(score) {
            if(score >= 39) return "9.0";
            if(score >= 37) return "8.5";
            if(score >= 35) return "8.0";
            if(score >= 32) return "7.5";
            if(score >= 30) return "7.0";
            if(score >= 27) return "6.5";
            if(score >= 23) return "6.0";
            if(score >= 19) return "5.5";
            if(score >= 15) return "5.0";
            return "Below 5.0";
        }

        function downloadHTML() {
            let startScreen = document.getElementById('start-screen');
            if(startScreen) startScreen.remove();
            let scoreScreen = document.getElementById('score-screen');
            if(scoreScreen) scoreScreen.remove();

            let htmlContent = "<!DOCTYPE html>\n" + document.documentElement.outerHTML;
            let blob = new Blob([htmlContent], { type: "text/html;charset=utf-8" });
            let link = document.createElement("a");
            let name = document.getElementById('display-name').innerText.replace(/\s+/g, '_');
            link.href = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
            link.download = `IELTS_Reading_Mastery_Custom_${name}.html`;
            document.body.appendChild(link);
            link.click();
            document.body.removeChild(link);
        }
    </script>
</body>
